  "description": "Performs the Anderson-Darling test for the composite hypothesis of normality, see e.g. Thode (2002, Sec. 5.1.4). Takes a table and a column reference to the values as input parameter. Thanks to Juergen Gross for the R implementation in the nortest library.",
  "tags": "function, statistics",
